notes: |
  Two classic margarita styles:

  Sweet (no triple sec): lime juice : simple syrup : tequila = 1 : 1 : 2, optionally add 1 part orange juice

  Classic (no simple syrup, less sweet, more balanced): tequila : triple sec : lime = 50 : 20 : 15, optionally add 20 frozen fruit of choice. Add 2 tsp sugar over ice before shaking.
